[
    {
        "text": "Hello! Welcome to Michael's Better Business English!",
        "startTime": 850,
        "endTime": 3800,
        "slowStartTime": 1450,
        "slowEndTime": 6000
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at how to interrupt.",
        "startTime": 4350,
        "endTime": 7200,
        "slowStartTime": 6650,
        "slowEndTime": 11100
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, this is quite a difficult skill for many Japanese business people...",
        "startTime": 8100,
        "endTime": 12350,
        "slowStartTime": 12350,
        "slowEndTime": 18700
    },
    {
        "text": "...and the main reason is culture difference.",
        "startTime": 12700,
        "endTime": 15500,
        "slowStartTime": 19250,
        "slowEndTime": 23400
    },
    {
        "text": "There are big differences between cultures in interrupting style.",
        "startTime": 16650,
        "endTime": 20200,
        "slowStartTime": 25100,
        "slowEndTime": 30500
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, in Japan, often it's not polite to interrupt.",
        "startTime": 21050,
        "endTime": 24650,
        "slowStartTime": 31750,
        "slowEndTime": 37200
    },
    {
        "text": "People instead wait for a long silence as an opportunity.",
        "startTime": 25200,
        "endTime": 28550,
        "slowStartTime": 38000,
        "slowEndTime": 43100
    },
    {
        "text": "However, in other cultures such as America or Europe,...",
        "startTime": 29450,
        "endTime": 32650,
        "slowStartTime": 44400,
        "slowEndTime": 49200
    },
    {
        "text": "...interrupting is much more accepted.",
        "startTime": 33000,
        "endTime": 35100,
        "slowStartTime": 49700,
        "slowEndTime": 52950
    },
    {
        "text": "And we often use much shorter silences.",
        "startTime": 35700,
        "endTime": 38150,
        "slowStartTime": 53750,
        "slowEndTime": 57500
    },
    {
        "text": "So, how can you do this?",
        "startTime": 38950,
        "endTime": 40700,
        "slowStartTime": 58650,
        "slowEndTime": 61250
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are four steps to help you.",
        "startTime": 41300,
        "endTime": 43450,
        "slowStartTime": 62150,
        "slowEndTime": 65400
    },
    {
        "text": "First, silence.",
        "startTime": 44350,
        "endTime": 46450,
        "slowStartTime": 66700,
        "slowEndTime": 70000
    },
    {
        "text": "As I mentioned, don't wait for a long silence.",
        "startTime": 47000,
        "endTime": 50550,
        "slowStartTime": 70700,
        "slowEndTime": 76100
    },
    {
        "text": "It might never happen in an English business meeting.",
        "startTime": 50750,
        "endTime": 53400,
        "slowStartTime": 76350,
        "slowEndTime": 80300
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, use body language.",
        "startTime": 54650,
        "endTime": 57600,
        "slowStartTime": 82150,
        "slowEndTime": 86650
    },
    {
        "text": "Leaning forward, making eye contact with the speaker, making a gesture,...",
        "startTime": 57850,
        "endTime": 62350,
        "slowStartTime": 87000,
        "slowEndTime": 93800
    },
    {
        "text": "...that's a good way to catch the attention of the speaker and help you interrupt.",
        "startTime": 62800,
        "endTime": 66700,
        "slowStartTime": 94400,
        "slowEndTime": 100250
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, project your voice.",
        "startTime": 68550,
        "endTime": 71150,
        "slowStartTime": 103050,
        "slowEndTime": 107000
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't speak down into the table.",
        "startTime": 71900,
        "endTime": 74100,
        "slowStartTime": 108050,
        "slowEndTime": 111400
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead, project your voice loudly and clearly,...",
        "startTime": 74450,
        "endTime": 77600,
        "slowStartTime": 111900,
        "slowEndTime": 116600
    },
    {
        "text": "...then there's more chance you'll interrupt successfully.",
        "startTime": 78050,
        "endTime": 81150,
        "slowStartTime": 117300,
        "slowEndTime": 122050
    },
    {
        "text": "And finally, use people's names.",
        "startTime": 82450,
        "endTime": 85600,
        "slowStartTime": 123850,
        "slowEndTime": 128700
    },
    {
        "text": "John, Mary, Michael.",
        "startTime": 85950,
        "endTime": 88321,
        "slowStartTime": 129150,
        "slowEndTime": 132478
    },
    {
        "text": "If you use somebody's name,...",
        "startTime": 88806,
        "endTime": 90423,
        "slowStartTime": 133302,
        "slowEndTime": 135571
    },
    {
        "text": "...people catch that very clearly and they will automatically stop speaking.",
        "startTime": 90450,
        "endTime": 95250,
        "slowStartTime": 135850,
        "slowEndTime": 143200
    },
    {
        "text": "So, for example, \"John, may I interrupt? How much did you say?\"",
        "startTime": 96050,
        "endTime": 100450,
        "slowStartTime": 144250,
        "slowEndTime": 150950
    },
    {
        "text": "Use these four techniques to help you interrupt successfully.",
        "startTime": 101200,
        "endTime": 105200,
        "slowStartTime": 152000,
        "slowEndTime": 158000
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck!",
        "startTime": 106050,
        "endTime": 107400,
        "slowStartTime": 159250,
        "slowEndTime": 161300
    }
]